---
title: Eggplant Korma with Tomatoes and Naan Bread
description: A mildly-spiced curry made with hearty potatoes and eggplant, bright tomatoes and spinach, and creamy coconut milk. Make sure to use the toasted naan to scoop up all that delicious goodness!
